<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Using IT in Practice Games</h2>

<p>IT scores 2 points without any premium square bonuses. As a 2-letter word, it is particularly useful in tight board positions where longer words cannot fit. Short words like IT shine in parallel plays — placing them adjacent to existing words so that every new tile forms a valid two-letter combination with the tiles beside it.</p>

